liber-research.com/about-us/</a><br />\n<br />\nFor English version, please see:<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/en/support-lrc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fen%2Fsupport-lrc%2F&d=RlDVVRIP0quLiKe1GH5koU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=aa3c946d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/en/support-lrc/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/en/about-liber-research-community/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fen%2Fabout-liber-research-community%2F&d=RlDVVRIP0quLiKe1GH5koU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=65c90c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/en/about-liber-research-community/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們在極短時間內製作網頁和眾籌計劃，資料或有未完善處，請多多包涵。如有任何查詢，歡迎pm本專頁或電郵至info@liber-research.com，感謝！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"辛苦了師兄"},{"pid":"f72fe21326c9080943a04b078643a76ac8458280","tid":921982,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:24:00.000Z","msg":"有冇睇火鳳燎原?<br />\n出糧草軍費既最蠢，打2打前線唔夠打就卷款逃逸。<br />\n妳養住班唔係作戰既人有咩用"},{"pid":"ab1dcfdb3b8d0634408ddd64f56df4072b92193c","tid":921982,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"社混? 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cd635bf8899095288b4e8a6cd54ee8f7be13c4","tid":921982,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"熱血狗仔隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8b04a36217a8606cf21dcea7e5789b0161f5e1","tid":921982,"uid":114750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T19:02:03.000Z","msg":"樓主課咗未"},{"pid":"be191de122cc181b0e7bd7b6e7778c0213eee2ea","tid":921982,"uid":67412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd8b04a36217a8606cf21dcea7e5789b0161f5e1"